        "translations": {
          "en": "A man came to the Messenger of God (may God bless him and his family) and said, 'O Messenger of God, what is knowledge?' He said, 'Silence.' He said, 'Then what?' He said, 'Listening.' He said, 'Then what?' He said, 'Memorization.' He said, 'Then what?' He said, 'Acting upon it.' He said, 'Then what, O Messenger of God?' He said, 'Spreading it.'",
